OL,3,CPassover UK: An ancient Jewish
OL,4,Cfestival in modern Britain
OL,6,FITV News reporter Sam Holder joined
OL,7,Ffamilies across the UK as they
OL,8,Fcelebrated Passover
OL,10,FThere is an old Jewish saying: "For
OL,11,Fevery two Jews, there are three
OL,12,Fopinions."
OL,14,FSo, it is no surprise that almost
OL,15,Fevery Jewish family in the UK has
OL,16,Ftheir own traditions when it comes to
OL,17,Fcelebrating the ancient festival of
OL,18,FPassover.
