OL,3,CPassover UK: An ancient Jewish
OL,4,Cfestival in modern Britain
OL,6,FFor thousands of years, the Jewish
OL,7,Fpeople have commemorated the Exodus -
OL,8,Fthe biblical story of Moses leading
OL,9,Fthe Israelites out of slavery from
OL,10,FEgypt.
OL,12,FIf you cannot quite remember the
OL,13,Fdetails from your RE classes, then it
OL,14,Fis basically the plot of the wildly
OL,15,Fpopular 1998 film "The Prince of
OL,16,FEgypt" (featuring an exceptional Oscar-
OL,17,Fwinning soundtrack with Whitney
OL,18,FHouston and Mariah Carey).
