OL,3,CPassover UK: An ancient Jewish
OL,4,Cfestival in modern Britain
OL,6,FIn Glasgow, I spoke with one of the
OL,7,Flast Chassidic (Ultra-Orthodox)
OL,8,Ffamilies left in Scotland, while in
OL,9,FLeeds I met a woman who had grown up
OL,10,FCatholic but now considers herself
OL,11,Fproudly Jewish.
OL,13,FWe filmed a massive open community
OL,14,F'Seder' (a ceremonial meal) in North
OL,15,FLondon and a tiny two-person one in
OL,16,FBelfast, where the community totals
OL,17,Fjust 400.
