OL,3,CPassover UK: An ancient Jewish
OL,4,Cfestival in modern Britain
OL,6,FThere are many misconceptions about
OL,7,Fthe Jewish community, especially that
OL,8,Feveryone has an Eastern European
OL,9,Flineage.
OL,11,FA particular highlight was filming
OL,12,Fwith Edwin, whose family lived in Iraq
OL,13,Ffor 2,000 years before fleeing in the
OL,14,F1970s amidst violent anti-semitic
OL,15,Frepression.
OL,17,FEdwin invited me to his special
OL,18,Finterfaith 'Seder,' which was held in
OL,19,FHebrew, English and - because of his
OL,20,Fpersonal heritage - Arabic.
