OL,3,CPassover UK: An ancient Jewish
OL,4,Cfestival in modern Britain
OL,6,FPassover is a story of survival in the
OL,7,Fface of adversity and for many British
OL,8,FJewish families, this year the
OL,9,Ffestival has taken on extra meaning
OL,10,Fwith rising antisemitism here in the
OL,11,FUK.
OL,13,FThe themes of liberation and captivity
OL,14,Falso have extra resonance amidst the
OL,15,Fglobal geopolitical landscape.
OL,17,FSome families symbolically laid out
OL,18,Fempty chairs in solidarity with the
OL,19,FIsraeli hostages taken on October 7th,
OL,20,Fwhile others spoke of how the story
OL,21,Freflects the suffering of Gazans.
