OL,3,CPassover UK: An ancient Jewish
OL,4,Cfestival in modern Britain
OL,6,FThat is because at its heart, this is
OL,7,Fa festival that is all about bringing
OL,8,Fpeople together. It is a chance for
OL,9,Ffamilies and friends, young and old,
OL,10,Fto sit around a table, eat together
OL,11,Fand sing together, while remembering
OL,12,Ftheir roots and celebrating their
OL,13,Ffreedom.
OL,15,FPassover UK: A Jewish Journey will air
OL,16,Fon ITV 1 and ITV X on Sunday at
OL,17,F10.15pm.
